</style><h2 id="outline__2" class="wp-block-heading">单元“Mori Mori Nyankomeshi” </h2><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img decoding="async" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/pw/ABLVV876OTKPXOT71NoDswA6FHKHinlOSDknm_skfoZiVBIruRZvh6aWRI6qgaY9nFql6CyY9_Eo3WaB-TXt0mPMPNFGsHopaxhVuVWbRFfGT3lOcOBZ_bGwSKVIesiCZdxC3lUMpFQC4cXeKny3dVpJ71fl=w1097-h617-s-no-gm" alt=""/><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">图片来源：新闻稿 © Vebop Project</figcaption></figure><p>一家新成立的公司，正在快速发展。<br>他们正在开发各种各样的东西来取悦猫，从罐头食品到猕猴桃。</p><p>有传言称，秘密研发成功的神秘烟雾导致员工变得毛茸茸的事故。最近，一座建筑物发生了爆炸。事实上，它经常爆炸。 </p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><div class="youtube"><iframe title="[预告片]VTuber办公室VebopProject第一代单元“Mori Mori Nyan Komeshi”首次亮相！" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/itf6YIs5eFw?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></div></div></figure><p></p><figure class="wp-block-table is-style-stripes"><table><tbody><tr><td>角色设计</td><td>尼玛（@n_n_nima）</td></tr><tr><td> X（推特）</td><td><a href="https://x.com/morinyan_info" target="_blank" rel="noopener" title="森森年科饭什">森森年科饭什</a></td></tr><tr><td>协作交付</td><td>2024年2月18日星期日 22:00~</td></tr></tbody></table></figure><p></p><h3 id="outline__2_1" class="wp-block-heading">拉拉科木天两</h3><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img decoding="async" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/pw/ABLVV860oa_2aVYm4I0xORCib6dvavvaEzjNvwNqW6vLEI7SguZ2rof3IaR9Vm0RpQTk4H8i7Ca3T2AaFzMoQoirSDQBxkvAv84wx5aI4n4Dpd7txW2Lz9wYq098vs1cQ7ATLJ5HqwkAEAryfhnsc6DQodQM=w768-h768-s-no-gm" alt=""/><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">图片来源：新闻稿 © Vebop Project</figcaption></figure><figure class="wp-block-table is-style-stripes"><table><tbody><tr><td>直播2D</td><td>不适用</td></tr><tr><td>YouTube</td><td> <a href="https://youtube.com/@larako_moriny